column5: This month, I sent the newsletter out a bit differently, so that my logo appears in the email and the links are easier to read.  Its a mass mail, so Im trying to see if everyone got it, and especially if it looks ok in your email.  If your not subscribed, you can subscribe here: http://www.ontariofishing.net/subscribe.html
Got it TJ...  It's much easier to read now.
